His birth name was Sun Wu, so if you hear someone referring

00:04:11.932 --> 00:04:17.572
to Sun Tzu, Sun zi, or Sun Wu, it’s all the same person.

00:04:18.282 --> 00:04:21.382
We’ll stick with Sun Tzu for the purposes of this episode.

00:04:22.552 --> 00:04:30.622
When Sun Tzu was alive China was in a period called the Warring States, ‘warring’ means ‘at war’.

00:04:31.742 --> 00:04:36.342
Sun was from the Wu state of China, which is in modern day

00:04:36.372 --> 00:04:40.512
Zhejiang province, to the east of the country, near to Shanghai.

00:04:41.712 --> 00:04:49.282
In modern China, this part of the country is one of the wealthiest, a heart of industry and power.

00:04:50.482 --> 00:04:54.862
But during the Warring States era it was far from it.

00:04:55.262 --> 00:05:02.462
It was very much a peripheral state, with the most important states to the north, closer to Beijing.

00:05:03.432 --> 00:05:06.892
You’ll note that I haven’t given specific dates for

00:05:07.212 --> 00:05:10.462
really anything here, because we simply don’t know.

00:05:11.552 --> 00:05:16.942
Historians believe that Sun Tzu existed around this time, and

00:05:17.102 --> 00:05:20.582
that he started writing down his thoughts on military strategy.

00:05:21.772 --> 00:05:27.322
Since the 5th century BC the text has been changed, edited by

00:05:27.492 --> 00:05:31.792
numerous different actors who added and removed parts of it.

00:05:32.622 --> 00:05:37.692
So even if it were Sun that first wrote it, the text that you would

00:05:37.692 --> 00:05:42.472
read today is almost certainly not the original written by Sun.

00:05:43.542 --> 00:05:48.602
But that doesn’t make it any less interesting, or any less worthwhile reading.

00:05:49.102 --> 00:05:51.202
Perhaps it makes it even more so.

00:05:51.912 --> 00:05:55.922
Indeed, when one thinks of some of the most widely read books in the

